params.sqlcmd: "SELECT " +" OPTION_ID " +"FROM " +" SYS_INSTALL_OPTIONS " +"WHERE " +" OPTION_ID = ? " +" AND INSTALL_FLG = 1"
"SELECT " +" COMPANY_CD " +"FROM " +" M_PLANT " +"WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" CODE " +"FROM " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE " +"WHERE " +" SYS_CLASS = ? " +" AND CLASS_CODE = 'PLANT_WEB'"
"SELECT " +" VALUE " +"FROM " +" SYS_PARAMETER " +"WHERE " +" NAME = ?"

"SELECT " +" UNSTOCK.ORGN_ODR_NO AS ORGN_ODR_NO, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.ADD_ODR_FLG) AS ADD_ODR_FLG, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.ODR_ACPT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS ODR_ACPT_DATE, " +" UNSTOCK.CUST_ODR_NO AS CUST_ODR_NO, " +" UNSTOCK.CUST_CD AS CUST_CD, " +" CUST.CUST_ANAME AS CUST_ANAME, " +" UNSTOCK.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD AS CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD, " +" UM.USER_NAME AS USER_NAME, " +" UNSTOCK.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD, " +" UNSTOCK.ITEM_NAME AS ITEM_NAME, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.DESINATED_DLV_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS DESINATED_DLV_DATE, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.ODR_UNIT_PRICE) AS ODR_UNIT_PRICE, " +" CUR.CUR_UNIT AS CUR_UNIT, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.ODR_QTY) AS ODR_QTY, " +" ITEM.STOCK_UNIT AS STOCK_UNIT, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.ODR_AMOUNT) AS ODR_AMOUNT, " +" UNSTOCK.TAX_CD AS TAX_CD, " +" UNSTOCK.REMARKS AS REMARKS, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.MODIFY_COUNT) AS MODIFY_COUNT " +"FROM " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK UNSTOCK, " +" M_CUST CUST, " +" M_ITEM ITEM, " +" USER_MST UM, " +" M_CUR CUR " +"WHERE " +" UNSTOCK.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND UNSTOCK.CUST_CD = CUST.CUST_CD(+) " +" AND UNSTOCK.COMPANY_CD = CUST.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" AND UNSTOCK.ITEM_CD = ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" AND UNSTOCK.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD = UM.USER_CD(+) " +" AND UNSTOCK.CURRNCY_CD = CUR.CUR_CD(+) " +" AND UNSTOCK.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND UNSTOCK.ODR_CMPLT_FLG = 0"
"SELECT " +" TAX_CD " +"FROM " +" M_TAX " +"WHERE " +" TAX_CD = ?"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK(ODR_NO, COMPANY_CD, CUST_ODR_NO, CUST_CD, ITEM_CD, ITEM_NAME, CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD, ODR_ACPT_PSN_CD, CURRNCY_CD, EXCH_TYP, DESINATED_DLV_DATE, ODR_UNIT_PRICE, ODR_QTY, ODR_AMOUNT, ODR_AMOUNT_EXCH_RATES, TAX_APPLY_TYP, TAX_CD, TAX_CALC_TYP, REMARKS, ODR_ACPT_DATE, ORGN_ODR_NO, ADD_ODR_FLG, ODR_CMPLT_FLG, ODR_CMPLT_DATE, DEL_FLG) " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), ?, TO_NUMBER(?), ?, TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), ?, TO_NUMBER(?), 0, NULL, 0)"

"SELECT " +" CUR_CD AS CUR_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(EXCH_TYP) AS EXCH_TYP, " +" TO_CHAR(TAX_APPLY_TYP) AS TAX_APPLY_TYP, " +" TO_CHAR(TAX_CALC_TYP) AS TAX_CALC_TYP, " +" TO_CHAR(DETAIL_ROUND_TYP) AS DETAIL_ROUND_TYP, " +" CUST_ANAME AS CUST_ANAME, " +" CUST_CD AS CUST_CD " +"FROM " +" M_CUST " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND CUST_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" UNSTOCK.ODR_NO " +"FROM " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK UNSTOCK, " +" T_SALES SALES " +"WHERE " +" UNSTOCK.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND UNSTOCK.SLIP_CD = SALES.SLIP_CD " +" AND SALES.SALES_TYP = 4"

"UPDATE " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK " +"SET " +" CUST_ODR_NO = ?, " +" CUST_CD = ?, " +" ITEM_CD = ?, " +" ITEM_NAME = ?, " +" CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD = ?, " +" DESINATED_DLV_DATE = TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" ODR_UNIT_PRICE = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" ODR_QTY = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" ODR_AMOUNT = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" ODR_AMOUNT_EXCH_RATES = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" TAX_CD = ?, " +" REMARKS = ?, " +" ODR_ACPT_DATE = TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" ORGN_ODR_NO = ?, " +" ADD_ODR_FLG = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" CURRNCY_CD = ?, " +" EXCH_TYP = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" TAX_APPLY_TYP = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" TAX_CALC_TYP = TO_NUMBER(?) " +"WHERE " +" ODR_NO = ?"
"UPDATE " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK " +"SET " +" DEL_FLG = 1 " +"WHERE " +" ODR_NO = ?"
"SELECT " +" USER_CD, " +" USER_NAME " +"FROM " +" USER_MST " +"WHERE " +" USER_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" UM.USER_CD, " +" UM.USER_NAME " +"FROM " +" USER_MST UM, " +" M_PLANT MP " +"WHERE " +" UM.USER_CD = ? " +" AND UM.PLANT_CD = MP.PLANT_CD " +" AND MP.COMPANY_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" ODR_NO " +"FROM " +" T_ODR " +"WHERE " +" ODR_NO = ? " +" AND DEL_FLG = 0"
"SELECT " +" ODR_CTL_NO " +"FROM " +" T_ODR " +"WHERE " +" ODR_CTL_NO = ? " +" AND DEL_FLG = 0"

"SELECT " +" DETAIL.ODR_H_NO " +"FROM " +" T_ODR DETAIL, " +" T_ODR_H HEAD " +"WHERE " +" DETAIL.ODR_H_NO = ? " +" AND DETAIL.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND DETAIL.ODR_H_NO = HEAD.ODR_H_NO " +" AND HEAD.SLIP_TYP <> 3"
"SELECT " +" ODR_CTL_NO " +"FROM " +" T_ODR " +"WHERE " +" ODR_CTL_NO = ? " +" AND COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND DEL_FLG = 0"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_ACPT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS ODR_ACPT_DATE, " +" ODR.CUST_ODR_NO AS CUST_ODR_NO, " +" CTL.CUST_CD AS CUST_CD, " +" ODR.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD AS CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD, " +" CTL.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.DESINATED_DLV_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS DESINATED_DLV_DATE, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_UNIT_PRICE) AS ODR_UNIT_PRICE, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_QTY) AS ODR_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_AMOUNT) AS ODR_AMOUNT, " +" ODR.TAX_CD AS TAX_CD, " +" UM.USER_NAME AS USER_NAME, " +" CUST.CUST_ANAME AS CUST_ANAME " +"FROM " +" T_ODR ODR, " +" T_ODR_CTL CTL, " +" USER_MST UM, " +" M_CUST CUST " +"WHERE " +" ODR.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND ODR.ODR_CTL_NO = CTL.ODR_CTL_NO " +" AND ODR.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD = UM.USER_CD(+) " +" AND CTL.CUST_CD = CUST.CUST_CD(+) " +" AND CUST.COMPANY_CD(+) = ? " +" AND CTL.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND ODR.DEL_FLG = 0"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.UNCNFM_CUST_ODR_CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS UNCNFM_CUST_ODR_CREATE_DATE, " +" ODR.CUST_ODR_NO AS CUST_ODR_NO, " +" ODR.CUST_CD AS CUST_CD, " +" ODR.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD AS CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD, " +" ODR.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.DESINATED_DLV_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS DESINATED_DLV_DATE, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.UNIT_PRICE) AS UNIT_PRICE, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_QTY) AS ODR_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_AMOUNT) AS ODR_AMOUNT, " +" ODR.TAX_CD AS TAX_CD, " +" UM.USER_NAME AS USER_NAME, " +" CUST.CUST_ANAME AS CUST_ANAME " +"FROM " +" T_ODR ODR, " +" USER_MST UM, " +" M_CUST CUST " +"WHERE " +" ODR.ODR_CTL_NO = ? " +" AND ODR.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD = UM.USER_CD(+) " +" AND ODR.CUST_CD = CUST.CUST_CD(+) " +" AND CUST.COMPANY_CD(+) = ? " +" AND ODR.DEL_FLG = 0"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_ACPT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS ODR_ACPT_DATE, " +" ODR.CUST_ODR_NO AS CUST_ODR_NO, " +" CTL.CUST_CD AS CUST_CD, " +" ODR.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD AS CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD, " +" CTL.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.DESINATED_DLV_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS DESINATED_DLV_DATE, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_UNIT_PRICE) AS ODR_UNIT_PRICE, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_QTY) AS ODR_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_AMOUNT) AS ODR_AMOUNT, " +" ODR.TAX_CD AS TAX_CD, " +" UM.USER_NAME AS USER_NAME, " +" CUST.CUST_ANAME AS CUST_ANAME " +"FROM " +" T_ODR ODR, " +" T_ODR_H HEAD, " +" T_ODR_CTL CTL, " +" USER_MST UM, " +" M_CUST CUST " +"WHERE " +" ODR.ODR_H_NO = ? " +" AND HEAD.ODR_H_NO = ODR.ODR_H_NO " +" AND ODR.ODR_CTL_NO = CTL.ODR_CTL_NO " +" AND ODR.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD = UM.USER_CD(+) " +" AND CTL.CUST_CD = CUST.CUST_CD(+) " +" AND CUST.COMPANY_CD(+) = ? " +" AND CTL.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND ODR.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND HEAD.SLIP_TYP <> 3"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.UNCNFM_CUST_ODR_CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS UNCNFM_CUST_ODR_CREATE_DATE, " +" ODR.CUST_ODR_NO AS CUST_ODR_NO, " +" ODR.CUST_CD AS CUST_CD, " +" ODR.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD AS CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD, " +" ODR.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.DESINATED_DLV_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS DESINATED_DLV_DATE, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.UNIT_PRICE) AS UNIT_PRICE, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_QTY) AS ODR_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(ODR.ODR_AMOUNT) AS ODR_AMOUNT, " +" ODR.TAX_CD AS TAX_CD, " +" UM.USER_NAME AS USER_NAME, " +" CUST.CUST_ANAME AS CUST_ANAME " +"FROM " +" T_ODR ODR, " +" USER_MST UM, " +" M_CUST CUST " +"WHERE " +" ODR.ODR_CTL_NO = ? " +" AND ODR.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND ODR.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD = UM.USER_CD(+) " +" AND ODR.CUST_CD = CUST.CUST_CD(+) " +" AND ODR.COMPANY_CD = CUST.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" AND ODR.DEL_FLG = 0"
"SELECT " +" CUST_CD " +"FROM " +" T_ODR " +"WHERE " +" ODR_CTL_NO = ? " +" AND COMPANY_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" CTL.CUST_CD " +"FROM " +" T_ODR ODR, " +" T_ODR_CTL CTL " +"WHERE " +" ODR.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND ODR.ODR_CTL_NO = CTL.ODR_CTL_NO " +" AND CTL.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND ODR.DEL_FLG = 0"
"SELECT " +" CUST_CD " +"FROM " +" T_ODR " +"WHERE " +" ODR_CTL_NO = ?"
"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(DECIMAL_FIG) AS DECIMAL_FIG " +"FROM " +" M_CUR " +"WHERE " +" CUR_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" SALES.CUST_ODR_NO " +"FROM " +" T_SALES_TEMP SALES, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK UNSTOCK " +"WHERE " +" UNSTOCK.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND SALES.SLIP_CD = UNSTOCK.SLIP_CD " +" AND SALES.SALES_TYP = 4"

"SELECT " +" UNSTOCK.ORGN_ODR_NO AS ORGN_ODR_NO, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.ADD_ODR_FLG) AS ADD_ODR_FLG, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.ODR_ACPT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS ODR_ACPT_DATE, " +" UNSTOCK.CUST_ODR_NO AS CUST_ODR_NO, " +" UNSTOCK.CUST_CD AS CUST_CD, " +" CUST.CUST_ANAME AS CUST_ANAME, " +" UNSTOCK.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD AS CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD, " +" UM.USER_NAME AS USER_NAME, " +" UNSTOCK.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD, " +" UNSTOCK.ITEM_NAME AS ITEM_NAME, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.DESINATED_DLV_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS DESINATED_DLV_DATE, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.ODR_UNIT_PRICE) AS ODR_UNIT_PRICE, " +" CUR.CUR_UNIT AS CUR_UNIT, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.ODR_QTY) AS ODR_QTY, " +" ITEM.STOCK_UNIT AS STOCK_UNIT, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.ODR_AMOUNT) AS ODR_AMOUNT, " +" UNSTOCK.TAX_CD AS TAX_CD, " +" UNSTOCK.REMARKS AS REMARKS, " +" TO_CHAR(UNSTOCK.MODIFY_COUNT) AS MODIFY_COUNT " +"FROM " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK UNSTOCK, " +" M_CUST CUST, " +" M_ITEM ITEM, " +" USER_MST UM, " +" M_CUR CUR " +"WHERE " +" UNSTOCK.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND UNSTOCK.CUST_CD = CUST.CUST_CD(+) " +" AND UNSTOCK.COMPANY_CD = CUST.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" AND UNSTOCK.ITEM_CD = ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" AND UNSTOCK.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD = UM.USER_CD(+) " +" AND UNSTOCK.CURRNCY_CD = CUR.CUR_CD(+) " +" AND UNSTOCK.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND UNSTOCK.ODR_CMPLT_FLG = 0 " +" AND UNSTOCK.COMPANY_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" 'AODR' || LPAD(SEQ_A_ODR.NEXTVAL, 10, 0) " +"FROM " +" DUAL"
"SELECT " +" CTL.CUST_CD " +"FROM " +" T_ODR ODR, " +" T_ODR_CTL CTL " +"WHERE " +" ODR.ODR_H_NO = ? " +" AND ODR.ODR_CTL_NO = CTL.ODR_CTL_NO " +" AND CTL.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND ODR.DEL_FLG = 0"
"SELECT " +" ITEM_NAME " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" ITEM_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" UNSTOCK.ODR_NO " +"FROM " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK UNSTOCK, " +" T_SALES SALES " +"WHERE " +" UNSTOCK.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND UNSTOCK.SLIP_CD = SALES.SHIP_DLV_H_NO " +" AND SALES.SALES_TYP = 4"
"SELECT " +" 1 " +"FROM " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC.\\"ODR_NO\\" = ? " +""
"SELECT " +" OWN_ORG_CD AS OWN_ORG_CD, " +" OWN_PERSON_CD AS OWN_PERSON_CD, " +" CUST_CD AS CUST_CD " +"FROM " +" M_CUST " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND CUST_CD = ?"
